rComments: Professor Montague is one of the best professors I have ever had. She is so nice and understanding. Her marking is very fair and she makes it easy to get a good grade in her classes. I would highly recommend taking any course taught by her. She is amazing.

She is an amazing prof. Always in a good mood, always willing to go above and beyond to help and truly loves teaching. Knows the course extremely well, so it is easy for her students to understand what she is explaining. She gives 3 pop quizzes throughout the semester but only keeps the grades for the 2 best which is nice too! Easy to get an A!
Always very helpful with feedback and available for office hours. Gets along well with students and makes class very interesting!

She is an awesome pro. She is understanding, respectful, and inspiring.  I didnt know too much about literature, but I am fairly certain that now I learnt a lot from her class, and I also got a huge interest in literature. 2 papers, 1 midterm, 3 quizes, and 1 final in one semester. her expectation for the papers is not too high.
